name: see • think • believe™ | Signature Gallery T-Shirt
description:
Over 2 1/2 years in the making, Healthy Rhythm Community Art Gallery is pleased to launch its Signature Gallery t-shirt, incorporating our tag-line, see • think • believe. The back of the t-shirt has gallery name/contact information, and a flaming tribal mask symbol!

Our see • think • believe™ t-shirt is 100% pre-shrunk Fruit of the Loom Heavy Duty cotton. It comes in black and is screen-printed with a beautiful Contact Blue color for lettering and symbols.

Adult sizes include Small, Medium, Large and XL.

This is a limited run, so get your t-shirt today.  And remember, see • think • believe™.  Anything is possible! 

*$5 of every t-shirt sold goes to support the Austin Harm Reduction Coalition in Austin, Texas. Check out their website at http://www.austinharmreduction.org/index.html.

name: eZra brown - The Journey CD/Album
description:
New York saxophonist eZra Brown brings "soul muzik-Muzik that forcez you 2 feel.... and not jus listen" in the moving work of Jazz music known as "The Journey". This great album finds eZra using his talent to bring a soulful and inviting vibe out of his instrument, one which is beautifully balanced by arrangements and a group of talented musicians who provide a range from upbeat dance, mellow ballads, smooth Jazz and Jazz-Rock fusion sounds. Sit back and allow your mind to absorb this expansive album as eZra leads the way to take your mind on a journey with his smooth approach on the sax. 

Song List
1. Afrojazz
2. Cookout
3. Sideways
4. The Journey
5. Her
6. Waterway
7. Flowerpot
8. Sendai

• Review courtesy of JR/Collectors Item
